events:
Vaishakh Krishna Paksha starts from 28th April and ends on 11th May,
Vaishakh Shukla Paksha starts from 12th May and ends on 26th May,
Zyeth Krishna Paksha starts on 27th May and ends on 10th June
Panchak starts on 4th and ends on 9th of this month

Zyeth Krishna Paksha starts from 27th May to 10th June,
Zyeth Shukla Paksha starts from 11th June to 24th June,
Aashaad Krishna Paksha starts from 25th June to 10th of July.
Panchak starts on 31st May and ends on 5th of this month
Panchak starts on 28th June and ends on 3rd July

Aashaad Krishna Paksha starts on 25th June and ends on 10th July,
Aashaad Shukla Paksha starts on 11th July and ends on 24th July,
Shravan Krishna Paksha starts from 25th July and ends on 8th August

Panchak starts on 28th June and ends on 3rd July,
Again Panchak starts on 25th July and ends on 30th July

Shravan Krishna Paksha starts on 25th July to 8th August,
Shravan Shukla Paksha starts on 9th August to 22nd August,
Bhadra Krishna Paksha starts from 23rd August to 7th September.
Panchak starts on 22nd and ends on 26th of this month

Punn Saath lies on 8th, 9th, 10th, 11th, 12th, 13th and 19th of this month,
Bhadra Krishna Paksha starts from 23th August to 7th September,
Bhadra Shukla Paksha starts from 8th September to 20th of September,
Ashwin Krishna Paksha starts on 21st September to 6th October
Panchak starts on 18th and ends on 23rd of this month
Panchak starts on 15th and ends on 20th of this month

Ashwin Krishna Paksha starts from 21st September to 6th October,
Ashwin Shukla Paksha starts from 7th October to 20th October,
Kartik Krishna Paksha starts from 21st October to 4th November
Panchak Starts on 11th and ends on 16th of this month

Kartik Krishna Paksha starts from 21st October and ends on 4th November,
Kartik Shukla Paksha starts from 5th November and ends on 19th November,
Maag Krishna Paksha starts on 20th November and ends on 4th December.
Panchak Starts on 9th and ends on 13th of this month

Maagh Krishna Paksha starts from 20th November to 4th December,
Maagh Shukla Paksha starts from 5th December to 19th of December,
Poh Krishna Paksha starts from 20th December to 2nd January.
Panchak Starts on 5th and ends on 10th of this month

Poh Krishna Paksha starts from 20th of December and ends on 2nd of January,
Poh Shukla Paksha starts from 3rd January and ends on 17th of January,
Maagh Krishna Paksha starts from 18th January and ends on 1st of February.
Panchak Starts on 2nd and ends on 6th of this month

Maagh Krishna Paksha starts from 18th January and ends on 1st of February,
Maagh Shukla Paksha starts from 2nd February and ends on 16th February,
Phalgun Krishna Paksha starts from 17th February and ends on 2nd of March.

Panchak Starts on 1st and ends on 5th of this month,
Also Panchak Starts on 28th March and ends on 2nd of April

Phalgun Krishna Paksha starts from 17th February and ends on 2nd of March,
Phalgun Shukla Paksha starts from 3rd March and ends on 18th of March,
Chaitra Krishna Paksha starts from 19th March and ends on 1st of April.

Panchak Starts on 28th March and ends on 2nd of April,
Also Panchak Starts on 24th April and ends on 29th of April

Chaitra Krishna Paksha starts from 19th March and ends on 1st of April,
Chaitra Shukla Paksha starts from 2nd April and ends on 16th of April,
Vaisakha Krishna Paksha starts from 17th April and ends on 30th April.
